  <brief_title>Studying Cardiac Tissue in Patients With Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Biologic Commonalities Associated With Degeneration in Function of Cardiac, Skeletal and Respiratory Muscles in Patients With Heart Failure.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
